  7→/**
  8→ * Walking Skeleton: Unified Identity Hub-and-Spoke
  9→ *
 10→ * Proves the thinnest vertical slice through the identity model:
 11→ * 1. Identity hub table exists and accepts records
 12→ * 2. Agent spoke table exists and accepts records
 13→ * 3. Spoke edges connect hub to spoke (identity_person, identity_agent)
 14→ * 4. Graph traversal works from identity -> spoke -> spoke record
 15→ *
 16→ * This is the FIRST test to enable. All other unified-identity tests
 17→ * remain skipped until this skeleton passes.
